{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id6b76c5c4-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s883j"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"883j"},"text":"§ 883j.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Ocean satellite data","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Administrator of the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (hereinafter referred to in this subtitle ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002029"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002029"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" as the “Administration”) shall take such actions, including the sponsorship of applied research, as may be necessary to assure the future availability and usefulness of ocean satellite data to the maritime community."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id6b76c5c5-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/272/tVI/s6082"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–272, title VI, § 6082","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-04-07"},"text":"Apr. 7, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/135"},"text":"100 Stat. 135","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id6b76c5c6-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id6b76c5c7-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id6b76c5c8-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This subtitle, referred to in text, is subtitle H (§§ 6081–6085) of title VI of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/272"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–272","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-04-07"},"text":"Apr. 7, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/135"},"text":"100 Stat. 135","children":[],"tail":", which enacted this section and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1530"},"text":"section 1530 of Title 15","children":[],"tail":", Commerce and Trade, amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t33/s883e"},"text":"section 883e of this title","children":[],"tail":" and sections 330e, 2903 and 2904 of Title 15, and repealed "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s2905"},"text":"section 2905 of Title 15","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of this subtitle to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id6b76c5c9-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"id6b76c5ca-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Functions of Secretary and other officers of Department of Commerce under this section that relate to the Office of Aeronautical Charting and Cartography to provide aeronautical charts, products, and services for safe and efficient navigation of air commerce transferred to Administrator of Federal Aviation Administration effective ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 2000","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s44721/c/2"},"text":"section 44721(c)(2) of Title 49","children":[],"tail":", Transportation."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id6b76c5cb-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Report on Satellite Oceanography","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/567/tI/s116"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–567, title I, § 116","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-29"},"text":"Oct. 29, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/4279"},"text":"106 Stat. 4279","children":[],"tail":", directed the Federal Coordinating Council for Science, Engineering, and Technology through the Committee on Earth and Environmental Sciences, in consultation with Federal, academic, and commercial users of remotely sensed data, to consider and develop findings and recommendations regarding the most urgent current needs of oceanographic researchers for remote sensing capabilities and remotely sensed data and the major goals of satellite oceanography for the next 10 years, and, not later than one year after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-29"},"text":"Oct. 29, 1992","children":[],"tail":", to submit to Congress a report which described the findings and recommendations of the Committee."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
